</p>

<p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
Packing your belongings in advance can also save time. Use strong boxes and clearly label each one with its contents and destination room. This will make unpacking much easier.
</p>

<p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
If you live in a busy part of Leicester, consider access and parking arrangements ahead of time. Informing your removal company of any restrictions will help avoid delays on the day.
</p>

<p class="text-gray-700">
Finally, keep essential items such as documents, chargers and toiletries easily accessible so you have everything you need during the move.
